summary: Hello there everyone! I know it has been a while and I am sorry about that. I have been swamped with commission work and college...
caption:
Hello there everyone!

I know it has been a while and I am sorry about that. I have been swamped with commission work and college has been kicking my ass but hopefully now that summer is here I will have time to do some requests.

I also wanna wish my followers a happy pride month! I did this quick edit of Retsuko with the new lesbian flag and I think that it looks really good. ^^

I will use this one in the future as I have heard some very nasty things about the creator of the all pink one.

Thank you all for sticking around for so long!

-Mod Dorito

summary: Aggretsuko Season 2 Is Coming to Netflix on June 14
title: Aggretsuko Season 2 Is Coming to Netflix on June 14
body:
Everyone’s favorite metalhead red panda will be back on Netflix this month!

Netflix recently announced on Twitter that Aggretsuko’s second season has a release date: June 14, 2019!

Everyone’s favorite overworked, underpaid, karaoke-loving red panda secretary is back and is rage-ier than ever before! Even though she is still surrounded by all of her friends, Retsuko will now be faced with more incompetent coworkers, the pressure of getting married and starting a family,…

summary: It’s so hard for me to pick a favorite Aggretsuko character tbh. I love all of them. (except Mr. Ton). I binged the entire first...
body:
It’s so hard for me to pick a favorite Aggretsuko character tbh. I love all of them. (except Mr. Ton). I binged the entire first season in one night and found myself heavily relating to Fenneko, Tsunoda, Retsuko, and Haida. That’s a pretty rare occurrence for me. I’m also able to get on board with some of the most popular ships (Retsuko x Haida and Fenneko x Tsunoda). In past fandoms, I usually enjoyed the rare pairs or “crack ships” as some folks call it lol. 

 I can’t wait to see what season two brings.

summary:
Sigh...
Sooooo, a few months ago, I started up a separate blog, for the Ikariverse. It’s called @asktheaggretsukofam. If you...
body:
Sigh…

Sooooo, a few months ago, I started up a separate blog, for the Ikariverse. It’s called @asktheaggretsukofam. If you want, check it out, you can ask questions to Retsuko, Haida, Ikari, even Fenneko.

Anyways, one such question came my way: “when is Ikari’s birthday?” Keep in mind, this was months ago. I kinda just decided to put a date I figured would be nice to have. I wrote something down in June, and left it at that. Just earlier today, I remembered that question, and decided to look back at it. After all, June IS coming up, figured I might as well get the party goin’.

And….well….

Sooooo, yeah. Ikari’s birthday is June 15th….one whole day after Season 2 drops. Figured I might as well tell y’all now, both in case people wanna give birthday wishes to the dear bon-bon boi, and…..well, to be honest, if Season 2 ends a certain way, I think I might need some of those, to cheer me up. 🙃
